Table 19. Supplemental data for 68 large county governments, 1995
Note:  Jurisdictions without data did not report for 1995, but data are available for prior years.
a/ Population data are from the Bureau of the Census, 1990 Decennial Census of Population and Housing.
b/ "Total general expenditure" excludes utilities, county-operated liquor stores, and insurance trust benefits.
c/ "General functions only" FTE excludes utilities and county-operated liquor stores.
